Section: games
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Debian Games Team <pkg-games-devel@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Uploaders: Michael DeGuzis <mdeguzis@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Homepage: https://github.com/libretro/mrboom-libretro

Package: libretro-mrboom
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: retroarch | libretro-frontend, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Libretro wrapper for Mr.Boom
 This wrapper makes Mr.Boom compatible with libretro, thus allowing its use with
 libretro frontends, such as RetroArch.
 .
 Mr.Boom is a Bomberman clone which supports up to 8 players and features like
 pushing bombs, remote controls and kangaroo riding.
